les per second By contrast the new NIST device monitors an optical frequency more than 100 000 times higher or about 1 quadrillion US cycles per second National Institute of Standards and Technology Division 847 325 Broadway Boulder CO 80305 Web site comments and general technical questions mailto lombardi boulder nist gov Michael Lombardi General NIST inquiries mailto inquiries nist gov Public Inquiries Unit 301 975 NIST 6478 TTY 301 975 8295
